LTh'aVH YBQSh NPhUrD BKL-ThVShYH YThGL'y.
L'a-YChPhTSh KSYL BThBVNH KY 'aM-BHThGLVTh LBV.
BBV'a-UrSh'y B'a GM-BVZ V'yM-QLVN ChUrPhH.
MYM 'yMQYM DBUrY PhY-'aYSh NChL NB'y MQVUr ChKMH.
Sh'aTh PhNY-UrSh'y L'a-TVB LHTVTh TShDYQ BMShPhT.
ShPhThY KSYL YB'aV BUrYB VPhYV LMHLMVTh YQUr'a.
PhY-KSYL MChThH-LV VShPhThYV MVQSh NPhShV.
DBUrY NUrGN KMThLHMYM VHM YUrDV ChDUrY-BTN.
GM MThUrPhH BML'aKThV 'aCh HV'a LB'yL MShChYTh.
MGDL-'yZ ShM YHVH BV-YUrVTSh TShDYQ VNShGB.
HVN 'yShYUr QUrYTh 'yZV VKChVMH NShGBH BMShKYThV.
LPhNY-ShBUr YGBH LB-'aYSh VLPhNY KBVD 'yNVH.
MShYB DBUr BTUrM YShM'y 'aVLTh HY'a-LV VKLMH.
UrVCh-'aYSh YKLKL MChLHV VUrVCh NK'aH MY YSh'aNH.
LB NBVN YQNH-D'yTh V'aZN ChKMYM ThBQSh-D'yTh.
MThN 'aDM YUrChYB LV VLPhNY GDLYM YNChNV.
TShDYQ HUr'aShVN BUrYBV YB'a-Ur'yHV VChQUrV.
MDYNYM YShBYTh HGVUrL VBYN 'yTShVMYM YPhUrYD.
'aCh NPhSh'y MQUrYTh-'yZ VMDVNYM KBUrYCh 'aUrMVN.
MPhUrY PhY-'aYSh ThShB'y BTNV ThBV'aTh ShPhThYV YShB'y.
MVTh VChYYM BYD-LShVN V'aHBYH Y'aKL PhUrYH.
MTSh'a 'aShH MTSh'a TVB VYPhQ UrTShVN MYHVH.
ThChNVNYM YDBUr-UrSh V'yShYUr Y'yNH 'yZVTh.
'aYSh Ur'yYM LHThUr'y'y VYSh 'aHB DBQ M'aCh.
